    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "So what led me to leave hostname overriding out of the production API was the direction [\"`This *should* be used for testing only.`\" where the relevant channel argument is defined](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/d848db1c06123d23888c705530fc012bcc7e9f35/include/grpc/impl/codegen/grpc_types.h#L147).\n\nAre you in a situation in which you need this capability for non-test production code? If you need this capability in a test, are you aware of the [`not_really_secure_channel` function](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/d848db1c06123d23888c705530fc012bcc7e9f35/src/python/grpcio/tests/unit/beta/test_utilities.py#L36) available to test code?\n"
